I"<h1 id="gith">Gith</h1>
<p><strong>Ability Score Increase.</strong> Your Intelligence score increases by 1.
Age. Gith reach adulthood in their late teens and live
for about a century.<br />
<strong>Size.</strong> Gith are taller and leaner than humans, with
most a slender 6 feet in height.<br />
<strong>Speed.</strong> Your base walking speed is 30 feet.<br />
<strong>Languages.</strong> You can speak, read, and write Common and Gith.
Subrace. There are two kinds of gith, githyanki and
githzerai. Choose one of these subraces.</p>
